[{"type":"{{","value":[["pagebanner"],["S-amer africa default banner.jpg"],["pgname=Altiplano"]]},"\nThe Bolivian ",{"type":"'''","value":["Altiplano"]}," is the area of the Andes above about 3500m in ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Bolivia"]]},". The altiplano stretches into neighbouring ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Altiplano (Peru)"],["Peru"]]}," and ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Argentina"]]},".\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Regions"]},"\n\n",{"type":"*","value":[{"type":"[[","value":[["Lake Titicaca"]]}]},{"type":"*","value":[{"type":"[[","value":[["La Paz (department, Bolivia)"],["La Paz"]]}]},{"type":"*","value":[{"type":"[[","value":[["Oruro (department)"],["Oruro"]]}]},{"type":"*","value":[{"type":"[[","value":[["Potosí (department)"],["Potosí"]]}]},"\n",{"type":"==","value":["Cities"]},"\n",{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"[[","value":[["La Paz (Bolivia)"],["La Paz"]]}]},{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Llallagua"]]}]},{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Oruro"]]}]},{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Potosí"]]}]},{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Tupiza"]]}]},{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Uyuni"]]}]},"\n",{"type":"==","value":["Other destinations"]},"\n\n",{"type":"*","value":[{"type":"[[","value":[["Chacaltaya"]]}," & ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Huayna Potosi"],["Huayna Potosí"]]}," — Bolivia's premiere ski resort, located right by the country's highest mountain"]},{"type":"*","value":[{"type":"[[","value":[["Madidi National Park"]]}]},{"type":"*","value":[{"type":"[[","value":[["Sajama National Park"]]}]},{"type":"*","value":[{"type":"[[","value":[["Salar de Uyuni"]]}]},{"type":"*","value":[{"type":"[[","value":[["Tiwanaku"]]}]},{"type":"*","value":[{"type":"'''","value":["Yungas Road"]}," (",{"type":"''","value":["Camino de la Muerte"]},") — infamous for being the most dangerous road in the world, in the Yungas Region, the notoriety of this road from ",{"type":"[[","value":[["La Paz"]]}," to ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Coroico"]]}," has turned it into a popular destination for international tourists, especially byciclists. Bolivia has finally finished the alternate paved route, so there is far less traffic on this road, and is at least a little safer for that."]},"\n",{"type":"==","value":["Understand"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Talk"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Get in"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Get around"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["See"]},"\n\n",{"type":"[[","value":[["File:Salar Uyuni au01.jpg"],["thumb"],["200px"],["The Salar de Uyuni salt lake"]]},"\n\n",{"type":"*","value":[" One of the highlights of this region is the ",{"type":"'''","value":["Salar de Uyuni"]},": 200 square miles of flat dazzling white salt at an altitude of 3700 metres. There are many tours of this salt lake from ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Uyuni"]]}," - or for a four day tour choose the one from ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Tupiza"]]}," near the ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Argentina"],["Argentine"]]}," border. There are many fascinating islands on the lake with giant cactii growing everywhere."]},"\n",{"type":"*","value":[" Another highlight in the bolivian altiplano are the highland lagunas in the southeast near the border to ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Chile"]]},". Most known is the Laguna Colorada ",{"type":"[","value":["http:\/\/www.travelpic.de\/Galerie_Bilder\/Suedamerika\/Bolivien\/Laguna_Colorada\/"]}," and also the Laguna Verde ",{"type":"[","value":["http:\/\/www.travelpic.de\/Galerie_Bilder\/Suedamerika\/Bolivien\/Laguna_Verde_y_Laguna_Blanca\/"]}," as well as the Árbol de Piedra."]},"\n",{"type":"===","value":["Itineraries"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Do"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Eat"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Drink"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Stay safe"]},"\nDuring the Bolivian winter time (in June and July) the temperatures can drop really low so bring good winter clothes and a sleeping bag suitable for temperatures bellow 0 degrees.\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Go next"]},"\n\n",{"type":"[[","value":[["WikiPedia:Altiplano"]]},"\n\n",{"type":"{{","value":[["geo"],["-16.0036"],["-69.6533"]]},"\n\n",{"type":"{{","value":[["IsPartOf"],["Bolivia"]]},"\n",{"type":"{{","value":[["outlineregion"]]},"\n\n\n\n",{"type":"[[","value":[["Commons:Category:Altiplano"]]}]